<br>
<br>
   His sticks moved in a frenzied blur as they threw out the rhythm to his march of the battle. Roll after roll he kept his feet marking time in place behind his warrior companion gone blood-thirsty from the duts and clangs of his drum creating a pulse quickening cadence. The warrior let out a roar as he dropped his first opponent and moved to the next whirling to dodge and parry with the little sense he had left in him. Move, strike, move, kill! The bard’s hands grew slick with sweat but he kept his pounding rhythm up. Swing after swing after merciless swing the warrior rolled the heads of the charging Iksars. The bard played louder as a line of invisible drums played with him, the sound of an army of bards. The warrior dogged the blade of an Iksar's and spun to land his blade in it’s lungs then freed it only to land it again in another’s. A devilish grin spread across his face as he moved his blade in time with the roar of the drums. Blocking another sword he rammed the hilt of his own into the attackers face. Turning to kick an on coming opponent then landing a punch under another Iksar’s ribs causing it to keel over. He could feel his blood rushing faster as he let out a crazed battle cry and lunged for the next. The bard fought his own battle, struggling to keep up the pace, beads of sweat formed on his forehead as he twisted his hands into a double stick shift then into another roll keeping his ally in the berserker frenzy that he was now in. The bard let out his own howl as his muscles flexed with his strain as he broke into the hardest lick of the song. The warrior laughed as he tore threw the now retreating line of enemies. He came down with rage upon the death seeking Iksars.<br>
<br>
<br>
  The two half elfs stood there, panting, the warrior slowly coming off his battle driven high. “There are more and more ever day Demetrey.” Warrior slowly said to the bard. “I know Therin, there really isn’t a whole lot we can do…just get the hell out of here.” <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showMessageRange?topicID=10.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showMessageRange?topicID=10.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showMessageRange?topicID=10.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a> <b>4</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showPrevMessage?topicID=10.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showNextMessage?topicID=10.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10.topic&index=80><img src=http://Auction.2y.net/user/paradisetheheretic/addreply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.emailToFriend?topicID=10.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.threadControl?topicID=10.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=10.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"